    <string name="onboard_title_1">What is a Transformer Zone?</string>
    <string name="onboard_desc_1">A transformer zone is a group of farms that share the same electricity supply line. When one farm loses power, all farms in the zone lose power too.</string>

    <string name="onboard_title_2">Report Power Status</string>
    <string name="onboard_desc_2">When you see power has returned to your field, tap \'POWER ON\'. This instantly alerts all other farmers in your zone. Together, you save hours of wasted trips!</string>

    <string name="onboard_title_3">Get Instant Alerts</string>
    <string name="onboard_desc_3">You will receive a notification the moment any farmer in your zone reports that power is restored. No more walking to the field to check!</string>

